SECURITIES, IMPAIRMENTS ARE RECOGNIZED BY WRITING DOWN THE INVESTMENT TO ITS

ESTIMATED FAIR VALUE, AS DETERMINED DURING THE COMPANYS QUARTERLY INTERNAL

REVIEW PROCESS.

