ESTIMATES IN THOSE RESERVES THROUGH A QUOTA-SHARE REINSURANCE AGREEMENT. THE

IMPACT OF THIS TRANSACTION IS NOT MATERIAL TO THE COMPANYS ONGOING OPERATIONS.

