ON APRIL 1, 2004, THE ST. PAUL TRAVELERS COMPANIES,

INC. FULLY AND UNCONDITIONALLY GUARANTEED THE PAYMENT OF ALL PRINCIPAL,

PREMIUMS, IF ANY, AND INTEREST ON CERTAIN DEBT OBLIGATIONS OF ITS SUBSIDIARIES

TPC AND TRAVELERS INSURANCE GROUP HOLDINGS INC. (TIGHI). THE GUARANTEES PERTAIN

TO THE $150 MILLION 6.75% NOTES DUE 2006, THE $400 MILLION 3.75% NOTES DUE

