RESPECTIVELY. THE QUALIFIED DOMESTIC PLAN ACCOUNTED FOR $1.69 BILLION AND $1.54

BILLION OF THE TOTAL ACCUMULATED BENEFIT OBLIGATION AT DECEMBER 31, 2005 AND

