RESTATED BYLAWS OF THE COMPANY, EFFECTIVE AS OF FEBRUARY 7, 2006, WERE FILED

AS EXHIBIT 3.2 TO THE COMPANYS FORM 8-K FILED ON FEBRUARY 10, 2006, AND ARE

INCORPORATED HEREIN BY REFERENCE.

